snippet.textDisplay: Wow fantastic the kind of music that should be highly promoted on such a platform. But still plenty of room for improvement.The camera movement , the exact focus of the camera at the right individual at the right moment. The "Aayi Aayi" and the "Harkalay" song were the most perfect example of camera movement and focus one could see of any folk song representing a tribe or community I would say. Perfect blend of light ,the focus on the singers and the people representing pashtun like the old man and woman, and the final scene of the pashtun dancing in a round small courtyard circumambulating around the courtyard's inner periphery with rain added a kind of realistic aura in the song.
snippet.textOriginal: Wow fantastic the kind of music that should be highly promoted on such a platform. But still plenty of room for improvement.The camera movement , the exact focus of the camera at the right individual at the right moment. The "Aayi Aayi" and the "Harkalay" song were the most perfect example of camera movement and focus one could see of any folk song representing a tribe or community I would say. Perfect blend of light ,the focus on the singers and the people representing pashtun like the old man and woman, and the final scene of the pashtun dancing in a round small courtyard circumambulating around the courtyard's inner periphery with rain added a kind of realistic aura in the song.
